Package com.rubynaxela.teaeditor.gui.components

Custom GUI widgets

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BrewingInstructionPanel
    BrewingInstructionPanel is a brewing recipe data input panel, a part of TeaBoxDialogPanel
    ColorPreviewBox
    ColorPreviewBox is a colored rectangle displayed at the bottom of a INCDataDialogPanel
    DefaultJScrollPane
    The DefaultScrollPane constructor serves as a shortened syntax for creating a new JScrollPane with fixed dimensions
    MenuBar
    The MenuBar class is an instance of JMenuBar; the menu displayed at the top of the window or in the system menu bar (depending on user's operating system)
    RGBColorChooser
    The RGBColorChooser class is an implementation of JColorChooser possesing only a part of JColorChooser's components
    StaticTable
    The StaticTable class is an implementation of JTable, configured in a way that enables only selection of a single row and disables any edits
